videos.headline: Franks connects with Swain for Gators' TD
videos.description: Feleipe Franks completes a pass to a wide-open Freddie Swain for a 15-yard touchdown to give Florida a 7-0 lead over Kentucky.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Franks connects with Swain for Gators' TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wagner makes incredible one-handed TD grab for Kentucky
videos.description: After the pass from Sawyer Smith was bobbled, Ahmad Wagner makes an incredibly difficult one-handed catch to score a 26-yard Kentucky touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wagner makes incredible one-handed TD grab for Kentucky) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kentucky's Smith dives in for 1-yard TD
videos.description: Sawyer Smith keeps it and plows his way into the end zone from the one yard line to give Kentucky a 14-7 lead over Florida.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kentucky's Smith dives in for 1-yard TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smith's bad pass gets picked and returned 72 yards
videos.description: Sawyer Smith throws an ill-advised pass that gets intercepted and returned 72 yards into Kentucky territory by Florida's Shawn Davis.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smith's bad pass gets picked and returned 72 yards) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Upshaw hauls in the 13-yard TD grab
videos.description: Keaton Upshaw leaps up to grab the 13-yard touchdown pass from Sawyer Smith to extend the Kentucky lead to 21-10 over Florida.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Upshaw hauls in the 13-yard TD grab) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Franks in tears while being carted off with injury
videos.description: Florida's Feleipe Franks gets taken down awkwardly and needs to be carted off the field with an injury.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Franks in tears while being carted off with injury) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trask's rushing TD gives Gators the lead
videos.description: Kyle Trask keeps the snap and runs four yards to the end zone as Florida retakes the lead 22-21.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Trask’s rushing TD gives Gators the lead) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kentucky's Poore misses potential go-ahead FG in crunch time
videos.description: Chance Poore misses a 35-yard kick wide right for the lead and Kentucky is forced to turn it over in the final minutes of the 4th quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kentucky's Poore misses potential go-ahead FG in crunch time) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hammond bursts free for 76-yard game-sealing TD
videos.description: Josh Hammond takes off to score a 76-yard touchdown as Florida seals a 29-21 win over Kentucky.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hammond bursts free for 76-yard game-sealing TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mullen saddened by loss of Franks
videos.description: Dan Mullen says he is saddened by the loss of Feleipe Franks, but explains why he is glad Kyle Trask had a chance to step into the spotlight.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Mullen saddened by loss of Franks) 2019/09/14 ESHEET
